  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a study to to compare traditional fibre wound swabs to more recently developed
      flocked swabs for the identification of Group A streptococcal pharyngitis in children
      presenting to a children's emergency department.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
